  "description": "A Roguelike deck builder where you try to adapt to the ultimate environment of randomness: a tossing coin. Create synergies, upgrade your cards, reevaluate your deck, sell your cards and buy more fitting cards - anything that keeps the coin bouncing back and forth.\n\nIngredients:\n\n• Monke cards (your playing cards)\n\n• Banana cards (upgrades monke cards)\n\n• Age of Monke cards (improve your runs)\n\n• Boss levels\n\n• Monke art that is bananas\n\n• Artistically crafted monke music\n\n50% skill, 50% luck, 100% Monke Brain",
  "description_short": "His monke brain is bored, needs stimulation. Use your superior brain to design the perfect deck of cards that makes number go up. Monke sees big number, monke stays happy.",
